high_descs: Turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and grab the bowl that is on the top shelf.  Close the fridge.
With the bowl in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.  Turn the water on to wash it.  Turn the water off and grab the bowl.
Turn and go to the brown shelf with the bowl in hand.
Place the bowl on the brown shelf second shelf down on the right hand side.
anns.task_desc: Wash bowl and place on shelf.

high_descs: Cross the room, hang a right at the edge of the counter and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Open the fridge, pick up the dirty container from the top shelf and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the container in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, hang a right at the fridge and walk to the rack of wooden shelves.
Put the clean container on the middle shelf on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean container on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right head to the fridge
Open the fridge pick up the dirty bowl then close it
Turn left walk forward toward the sink
Put the bowl in the sink and fill in water
Turn left walk straight then turn right face the shelf rack
Put the bowl with water on the second level of the shelf rack
anns.task_desc: Put the clean bowl with water on  the shelf rack
